quran[9{c,v,t}:
12,44,"logon ne kaha"" yeh to pareshan khowaboon ki baatein hain aur hum is terhan ke khowaboon ka matlab nahi jantay """
12,45,"unn do qaidyoun mein se jo shakhs bach gaya tha aur ussay aik muddat daraaz ke baad ab baat yaad aayi, uss ne kaha"" mein aap hazraat ko is ki taweel batata hon, mujhe zara ( qaid khanaay mein yousuf ke paas ) bhaij degiye """
12,46,"is ne ja kar kaha"" yousuf, ae saraapaa raasti, mujhe is khawab ka matlab bta ke saat mouti ghaein jin ko saat dubli ghaein kha rahi hain aur saat balen hari hain aur saat sookhi shayad ke mein unn logon ke paas jaoon aur shayad ke woh jaan len """
12,47,"yousuf ne kaha"" saat Bar seen taq lagataar tum log khaiti baari karte raho ge is douran mein jo faslein tum katu unn mein se bas thora sahissah, jo tumhari khoraak ke kaam aeye, nikalu aur baqi ko is ki balon hi mein rehne do"
12,48,phir saat baras bohat sakht ayen ge uss zamane mein woh sab ghalla kha liya jaye ga jo tum uss waqt ke liye jama karo ge agar kuch bachay ga to bas wohi jo tum ne mehfooz kar rakha ho
12,49,"is ke baad phir aik saal aisa aeye ga jis mein baaraan rehmat se logon ki faryaad rassi ki jaye gi aur woh ras nachorain ge """
12,50,"badshah ne kaha usay mere paas lao magar jab Shahi Farstada yousuf ke paas pouncha to is ne kaha"" apne rab ke paas wapas ja aur is se pooch ke unn aurton ka kya maamla hai jinhon ne apne haath kaat liye thay? mera rab to un ki makkari se waaqif hi hai """
12,51,"is par badshah ne un aurton se daryaft kya"" tumhara kya tajurbah hai uss waqt ka jab tum ne yousuf ko rijhaane ki koshish ki thi ?"" sab ne yak zabaan ho kar kaha"" Haa- sha- Allah, hum ne to uss mein badi ka shaiyba taq nah paaya"" Aziz ki biwi bol uthi"" ab haq khil chuka hai, woh mein hi thi jis ne uss ko پھسلانے ki koshish ki thi, be shak woh bilkul sacha hai """
12,52,"( yousuf ne kaha )"" iss se meri gharz yeh thi ke ( Aziz ) yeh jaan le ke mein ne darparda is ki khayanat nahi ki thi, aur yeh ke jo khayanat karte hain un ki chalon ko Allah kamyabi ki raah par nahi lagaata"
